STATUS_INITIALIZED

public static final MapViewEventType STATUS_INITIALIZED
Indicates same as OnStatusChangedListener.STATUS.INITIALIZED. When you use this library you have to use this to listen to the map initialization event. If you override the listener elsewhere in your app this will not get called and will cause errors within this library.
